{
  "stem": "9963.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you had to actually fight for your rights, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they would leave you alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had different misagreement, different fights, and things like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the worst thing was when we came to the third grade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The third grade was very hard to pass, because you started learning different things like the geography, [NON-ENGLISH], and all that items when was very hard to pass.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Polish boys-- they're not too smart on that, and they couldn't pass the third grade.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because they couldn't pass, they flunk about two, three years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we came in, we were little boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, we were only about eight years or nine years, some of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When they were already three, four years older from us, so they knew already the routine-- when they can pick on us, when they can beat us up, and things like this.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one time the teacher took us on the out someplace over there to visit some things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the way back-- this was an outing-- on the way back he went home, because he lived not far from there, and let us students by ourselves.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were prepared with knives and with stones to beat us up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my luck was, you know, that I was with another boy what was very, very strong.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole family-- they were very, very strong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no matter how little he was, but he was a very strong young man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the fight starts on me and the other boy were fighting about 10 or 15 guys.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Luckily enough, we didn't got hurt, only I got a cut with a knife right here, what I have still the mark here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we beat up the other guys.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
